#: install.php:346
msgid ""
"The \"canceldispositionenabled\" option in Asterisk configures Call Detail "
"Records (CDR) to distinguish calls that were cancelled (abandoned by the "
"caller before being answered) from other unanswered calls. When this option "
"is enabled, calls ending due to the caller hanging up during ringing will "
"have the disposition \"CANCEL\" instead of the default \"NO ANSWER\". This "
"option is supported on Asterisk version 20 and above."
msgstr ""

